This product bundles NATS server (https://github.com/nats-io/nats-server),
which is available under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

  Copyright The NATS Authors
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

The bundled NATS server binary is fetched at release-build time directly
from the official NATS server GitHub release for each target platform,
verified against the upstream SHA256SUMS, and shipped inside the release
tarball alongside the hyerix-natsfixture binary. The pinned NATS server
version for any given hyerix-natsfixture release is recorded in
.github/workflows/release.yml (env.NATS_SERVER_VERSION) and is reported
at runtime by `hyerix-natsfixture --version`.
